text: Soyeon: Ah..I was unconscious for a while...
Soyeon: Wait, where am I?
Snakyneck: You arrived?
Soyeon: Huhhhh...?
Snakyneck: Haven't we met before like this in your dream?
Snakyneck: I was really impressed by your heartless free ride in your group project and I was going to invite you as a guest lecturer of the Hell Uni...
Snakyneck: However you were stunned to see me and ran away...
Soyeon: Oh... you're the ghost I met...!!

Snakyneck: I was most impressed
when you lied that your parent's cousin passed away to skip the team meeting.
Soyeon: I feel very regretful about that...

Snakyneck: However, you're very different from the people
who become villans in group projects.

Snakyneck: You've participate in group project very faithfully
barring that one escape.

Snakyneck: You even submitted the physics report instead of your teammate.
Even your fever went up to 39 degrees huh?
Soyeon: It would be awful to both forget my report and screw up my midterm...

Snakyneck: Anyway, I wanted to write a graduation thesis
on human reflection and introspection with you as the subject matter,
and I just knocked you down here while you were suffering from a high fever.
Soyeon: You're mean as fuck...
Snakyneck: I'm going to observe you when you were stuck in the hell.
Soyeon: Can I go back to the real world after observation?
Snakyneck: Im not sure...
Soyeon: You're very mean meaning to kill me...
Snakyneck: ??
Soyeon: Ah, as the word 'mean' has both meaning of intent and being evil, so...
Snakyneck: ...
Snakyneck: Anyway please help me. I have to graduate.
Soyeon: Wait this is all too sudden...

Snakyneck: You are too weary and sick to run away this time,
don't you think?

Snakyneck: I know your parents went to Jejudo
so help me until they come back.
Soyeon: Damn... this is some bad timing...
Snakyneck: Please help a poor graduate student, will you?
Soyeon: Don't fuck with me, my sister will be off work soon and she could call 119 for me. (*911)
Snakyneck: Doesn't your sister work overnight a lot these days?
Snakyneck: So help me until night.
Soyeon: No! Go away! Somebody help!
Snakeyneck: You better not escape from me...!
